OL,6,FThe woman who attacked Miss Arthurs `
OL,7,F25-year-old Emily Williams ` has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to five years in prison for
OL,9,Finflicting grievous bodily harm with
OL,10,Fintent.
OL,12,FWilliams continues to deny she slashed
OL,13,Fher victim with a glass and said she
OL,14,Fdoes not know how the horrific
OL,15,Finjuries were caused.
