OL,6,FA judge described what she did as
OL,7,F"wicked almost beyond belief". heard
OL,8,Fthe assault took place in the toilets
OL,9,Fof the Peppermint bar in Swansea's
OL,10,FWind Street on Thursday 17 November
OL,11,F2022 ` a day which saw crowds in the
OL,12,Fcity centre celebrating Beaujolais Day.
OL,14,FJust before 6pm Miss Arthurs was in
OL,15,Fthe toilets when Williams came in and
OL,16,Fstarted shouting at her.
OL,18,FWilliams then smashed the glass she
OL,19,Fwas carrying and used the weapon to
OL,20,Fslash her victim's face.
