OL,6,FMiss Arthurs said: "I was putting on
OL,7,Flipstick in the mirror when I heard a
OL,8,Fvoice with an angry tone shouting
OL,9,Fsomething like: 'Who do you think you
OL,10,Fare?'
OL,12,F"I heard a glass smashing and I turned
OL,13,Faround and saw a woman with blonde
OL,14,Fhair and a glass in her hand. I saw
OL,15,Fthe glass coming towards my face.
OL,17,F"It was all so quick. I felt something
OL,18,Fcold cutting into my face. I knew it
OL,19,Fwas bad."
