OL,6,FThe court heard Miss Arthurs is
OL,7,Fcurrently under the care of the burns
OL,8,Fand plastics department at Morriston
OL,9,Fand faces further procedures and
OL,10,Ftreatments in the coming years.
OL,12,FMiss Arthurs, who lives in
OL,13,FCwmrhydyceirw in Swansea, said: "It
OL,14,Ftook 15 months for this to come to
OL,15,Ftrial. For those 15 months I think I
OL,16,Fwas in shock ` like autopilot.
OL,18,F"It is only now I am coming to terms
OL,19,Fwith everything. I am going to have
OL,20,Fthis scar for the rest of my life ` I
OL,21,Fknow that.
