OL,6,F"In the past I always avoided
OL,7,Fconflicts and I felt like I was in
OL,8,Fcontrol. This has just knocked me and
OL,9,Fshown me you are not in control of
OL,10,Fwhat happens.
OL,12,F"It was a random, unprovoked attack
OL,13,Fdone for no reason. This has changed
OL,14,Fmy outlook on life."
