OL,6,FThe mum-of-one said she has felt
OL,7,Funable to return to her work as a self-
OL,8,Femployed cleaner following the assault
OL,9,Fand has also given up her role in the
OL,10,FArmy Reserves where she was training
OL,11,Fto be a driver with the Royal Logistic
OL,12,FCorps.
OL,14,FIn an impact statement that was read
OL,15,Fto the court by prosecution barrister
OL,16,FAlycia Carpanini during the hearing,
OL,17,FMiss Arthurs said the events of that
OL,18,FNovember afternoon "changed my life
OL,19,Fforever".
