OL,6,FShe said she had been an outgoing
OL,7,Fperson, but now has overwhelming
OL,8,Fanxiety and panic attacks, "cries most
OL,9,Fdays" and struggles to sleep most
OL,10,Fnights, and has been left endlessly
OL,11,Fasking the question: "Why me?".
OL,13,FShe said she is now constantly on edge
OL,14,Fand struggles to trust people and said
OL,15,Fshe "despises" seeing the scar or
OL,16,Ftouching it, which she had to do
OL,17,Fseveral times a day as part of her
OL,18,Frehabilitation.
