OL,6,FEmily Monica Williams, of
OL,7,FCarmarthenshire, had previously been
OL,8,Fconvicted at trial of inflicting
OL,9,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent when
OL,10,Fshe appeared in the dock for
OL,11,Fsentencing.
OL,13,FShe has no previous convictions but
OL,14,Fhas a youth caution for possession of
OL,15,Fthe drug speed from 2013.
