OL,6,FDefending Jon Tarrant said Williams
OL,7,Fwas the sole carer for two young
OL,8,Fchildren and said references before
OL,9,Fthe court show "a very different side"
OL,10,Fto Williams than the one seen during
OL,11,Fthe trial process.
OL,13,FJudge Huw Rees told Williams what she
OL,14,Fhad done to a stranger in the toilets
OL,15,Fof Peppermint had been "wicked almost
OL,16,Fbeyond belief" and it had left her
OL,17,Fvictim with an "obvious disfiguring
OL,18,Fwound" to her face.
OL,20,FThe defendant was sentenced to five
OL,21,Fyears in prison.
